Motopanser DQ Variant was created/rendered by Thobie Buntaran a.k.a. Loreng on 21 October 2021, Mantrijeron, Yogyakarta, Indonesia.

A hybrid of a motorcycle & panzer with ultra biodynamic & mechanical design, with a top speed of 300000 km/s or 186000 mi/s.
Designed in the 3020s and manufactured in Santuari Lab by Loreng, this automobile species is specially made for interplanetary transportation & frontline battles.
This species can reproduce both in sexual and asexual (parthenogenesis) in times when reproductive opportunities are limited.

  A DQ Variant specializes in destroying the long straight enemy defense line on the battlefields.
